**Python #1.** Recursive DFS with memoization. Here, we consider each house and (i) either skip it (ii) or rob and skip the next one. This way, we will make a branching decision at every house, thus, exploring all possible scenarios of massive robbery. Space complexity is linear: **O(N)**.
