Because we cannot store all the index for each distinct element, so we need O(n) time for each call. Say we have 4 of '1' in the array, when we first time meet '1', we take this index with probability of 1, then 1/2 for the second time, 1/3 for the third time, 1/4 for the 4th time. This is the basic idea.

So overall we use O(n) time and O(1) space.

